<body><p><span style='color: rgba(52, 52, 52, 1.000000); font: 14px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>虽然它和普通的</span><span style='color: rgba(52, 52, 52, 1.000000); font: 14px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '> css </span><span style='color: rgba(52, 52, 52, 1.000000); font: 14px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>类相似，可以为已有的元素添加样式，但是它只有处于</span><span style='color: rgba(52, 52, 52, 1.000000); font: 14px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '> dom </span><span style='color: rgba(52, 52, 52, 1.000000); font: 14px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>树无法描述的状态下才能为元素添加样式，所以将其称为伪类。</span></p></body>
</html>
</richcontent>
